Then there is the point I was making in that 2014 Article: in the analog wo=
rld one=E2=80=99s choices were constrained to what was geographically acces=
sible; on the Internet everything is accessible, so why wouldn=E2=80=99t yo=
u choose to consume the =E2=80=9Cbest=E2=80=9D stuff? In other words, there=
